# Solana RPC the widget talks to (HTTP endpoint; WS is derived https→wss).
# Use a Helius endpoint (https://mainnet.helius-rpc.com/?api-key=...) — the
# widget resolves token symbols/icons via the Helius DAS API, so metadata
# fetches 403 on the public RPC (the widget still works, just unlabeled
# tokens). The public RPC is also heavily rate-limited.
NEXT_PUBLIC_RPC_URL=https://api.mainnet-beta.solana.com
